/></blockquote><br />\n有時候廚房的確會咁樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但做得打邊爐居然無一早搶出黎溶雪就過份左"},{"pid":"8b3124fe1d5f09214aa4ac3718f9a1b71489bb78","tid":133660,"uid":59546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:21:57.000Z","msg":"有冇比錢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話我低要求都你咁講 講真咁既價錢係食d咁既質素架啦 <br />\n<br />\n利申：係上水名都食 個姐姐仲要係講普通話 廣東話唔識聽加唔識講"},{"pid":"08a10c06243e9aa1eff1bbcdf9deb03a0555bf65","tid":133660,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:22:44.000Z","msg":"有冇俾錢"},{"pid":"71e21856b5167916d626f81fb6f105d3971c1f81","tid":133660,"uid":82747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T19:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畀個五我</blockquote><br />\n唔比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015cbf4fd6520fdeeca7fecbec71aa82aac5e14c","tid":133660,"uid":12957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T23:15:19.000Z","msg":"啲阿姐都幾貼心呀<br />\n見你等咁耐好心急叮埋俾你食住先呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75dbfbcee070a37ef55e4206e3916fbfd7d8b3e9","tid":133660,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T23:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n丁佢解凍都比佢諗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時候廚房的確會咁樣做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但做得打邊爐居然無一早搶出黎溶雪就過份左</blockquote><br />\n要有幾趕先會叮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用水沖都好快解到凍"},{"pid":"38b8aee51ba0243cbc46127758c0f6931b538147","tid":133660,"uid":52684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"